ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select z.* from ( select PenNumber = p.PenNumber ,PenName = lp.LocationName ,PrimaryPenType = pt.PenTypeName ,AvgPenCount = ds.AvgPenCount ,ReportDate = ds.ReportDate ,CompanyName = c.CompanyName ,DropActualAF = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropAFUnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) ,DropActualDM = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropDMUnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) ,DropActualAFPerHead = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropAFUnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) / NULLIF(ds.AvgPenCount, 0) ,DropActualDMPerHead = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropDMUnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) / NULLIF(ds.AvgPenCount, 0)
,CleanupAF = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(NULLIF(cs.AFUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) ,CleanupDM = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(NULLIF(cs.DMUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) ,CleanupAFHd = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(NULLIF(cs.AFUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) / NULLIF(ds.AvgPenCount, 0) ,CleanupDMHd = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(NULLIF(cs.DMUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) / NULLIF(ds.AvgPenCount, 0)
,TotalAF = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropAFUnitQuantity - ISNULL(cs.AFUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) ,TotalDM = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropDMUnitQuantity - ISNULL(cs.DMUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) ,TotalAFPerHead = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropAFUnitQuantity - ISNULL(cs.AFUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) / NULLIF(ds.AvgPenCount, 0) ,TotalDMPerHead = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ds.DropDMUnitQuantity - ISNULL(cs.DMUnitQuantity, 0), c.MediumMeasurementType) / NULLIF(ds.AvgPenCount, 0) from ( select p.PenGID ,AvgPenCount = AVG(CONVERT(real, pcc.PenCount)) ,ReportDate = fs.InstanceDate ,DropAFUnitQuantity = SUM(itd.AFUnitQuantity) ,DropDMUnitQuantity = SUM(itd.DMUnitQuantity) ,DropAFUnitQuantityPerHead = SUM(itd.AFUnitQuantity / NULLIF(pcc.PenCount, 0)) ,DropDMUnitQuantityPerHead = SUM(itd.DMUnitQuantity / NULLIF(pcc.PenCount, 0)) ,DropFifoCost = SUM(itd.FifoCost) ,DropTargetAFUnitQuantity = SUM(itd.TargetAFUnitQuantity) ,DropTargetDMUnitQuantity = SUM(itd.TargetDMUnitQuantity) from Pen p join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.LocationGID = p.LocationGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join (select it.TransactionSourceGID ,AFUnitQuantity = SUM(it.UnitQuantity) ,DMUnitQuantity = SUM(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct) ,FifoCost = SUM(it.FifoCost) ,StartDT = MIN(dateadd(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT)) ,TargetAFUnitQuantity = SUM(it.TargetUnitQuantity) ,TargetDMUnitQuantity = SUM(it.TargetUnitQuantity * it.DMPct) from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionType = 1 group by it.TransactionSourceGID) itd on itd.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID cross apply (select top 1 PenCount = pcc.[Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = p.PenGID and pcc.InventoryItemType = 3 and pcc.CreatedDT <= itd.StartDT order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) pcc group by p.PenGID, fs.InstanceDate ) ds join Pen p on p.PenGID = ds.PenGID join Location lp on lp.LocationGID = p.LocationGID join Company c on c.CompanyGID = lp.CompanyGID cross apply ( select top 1 pt.PenTypeName from PenType pt join PenPenType ppt on ppt.PenTypeGID = pt.PenTypeGID and ppt.PenGID = p.PenGID where pt.Inactive = 0 and ppt.Inactive = 0 and ppt.IsPrimary = 1) pt left join ( select p.PenGID ,ReportDate = CONVERT(date, it.TransactionDT) ,AFUnitQuantity = SUM(it.UnitQuantity) ,DMUnitQuantity = SUM(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct) from ManualFeeding mf join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mf.ManualFeedingGID join Location fl on fl.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID join Pen p on p.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID where mf.ManualFeedingType = 1 and fl.LocationType = 1 group by p.PenGID, CONVERT(date, it.TransactionDT)) cs on cs.PenGID = ds.PenGID and cs.ReportDate = ds.ReportDate ) z where 1=1</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
